name: iep-printing
description: iep-printing is a custom plugin for PowerSchool that works with [iep-printing-php](https://github.com/IronCountySchoolDistrict/iep-printing-php) to bring an IEP solution to PowerSchool. Track IEPs for students and Print [FormBuilder](http://www.accelaschool.com/formbuilder) forms.
author: Iron County School District
